== 發行 ==
電影在[[美國|美國]]發行於2016年7月1日<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Tom Hanks-Steven Spielberg Cold War Thriller Set for Oct. 16, 2015|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tom-hanks-steven-spielberg-cold-war-thriller-set-for-oct-16-2015-1201221269/|accessdate=June 6, 2014|work=Variety|date=June 16, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807120624/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/tom-hanks-steven-spielberg-cold-war-thriller-set-for-oct-16-2015-1201221269/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並由[[華特迪士尼工作室電影|華特迪士尼工作室電影]]發行於世界各地，除了歐洲、非洲和中東地區是由[[夢工廠|夢工廠]]負責。[[夢工廠|夢工廠]]的合作夥伴{{link-en|Reliance Entertainment|Reliance Entertainment}}將負責印度的發行權，而Entertainment One則定於2016年7月22日在[[英國|英國]]上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Steven Spielberg’s ‘The BFG’ Primed for U.K. Release With eOne|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/steven-spielbergs-the-bfg-primed-for-u-k-release-with-eone-1201261149/|accessdate=July 12, 2014|work=Variety|date=July 11, 2014|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721145552/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/steven-spielbergs-the-bfg-primed-for-u-k-release-with-eone-1201261149/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《吹夢巨人》獲得了普遍好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據305位專業影評人持有74%的新鮮度，平均得分6.7/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_bfg_2016/?search=BFG |title=The BFG (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=May 13, 2016 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020154626/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_bfg_2016/?search=BFG |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到66分，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.4分，正面評價居多<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bfg |title=The BFG reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=May 15, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113429/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bfg |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
美國於2016年7月1日上映，首映週末票房僅1960萬美元，位居當週票房排名第四，表現不佳。[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]認為，這是一個可怕的開始，因電影的成本高達1.4億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/07/02/box-office-disneys-the-bfg-earns-not-so-huge-7m-friday/#415ea2a85279|title=Box Office: Disney's 'The BFG' Earns Not-So-Huge $7M Friday|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=July 2, 2016|accessdate=July 3, 2016|archive-date=2018-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714024037/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/07/02/box-office-disneys-the-bfg-earns-not-so-huge-7m-friday/#415ea2a85279|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DEADopening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/independence-day-box-office-legend-of-tarzan-the-purge-election-year-the-bfg-1201782489/|title=‘Dory’ Dominates, ‘Tarzan’ Improves, ‘Purge’ Excels As ‘BFG’ Falls: July 4th Weekend B.O. – Sunday Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=July 3, 2016|accessdate=July 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704125452/http://deadline.com/2016/07/independence-day-box-office-legend-of-tarzan-the-purge-election-year-the-bfg-1201782489/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，台灣則於8月11日上映，首映週末獲466萬新台幣位居當週第三，次週獲259萬降至第六，上映第3週以120萬位居第九。

